<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Help</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/image/Weather.webp">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <script src="./js/app.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="main-content">
        {{>header}}

        <h4>Weather Help & FAQ</h4>

        <h2>❓ How Can I Check the Weather?</h2>
        <p>Simply enter your city or location in the search bar and hit <strong>"Search"</strong> to get the
            latest forecast.</p>

        <h2>🌡️ What Information Do I Get?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Current Temperature & Feels Like:</strong> 🌡️</li>
            <li><strong>Weather Condition & Icon:</strong> ☀️🌧️🌩️</li>
            <li><strong>Chance of Rain:</strong> 🌧️</li>
            <li><strong>Sunrise & Sunset Times:</strong> 🌅🌇</li>
            <li><strong>Wind Speed & Direction:</strong> 🌬️</li>
            <li><strong>Air Quality Index:</strong> 🌍</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>🔄 How Often is the Weather Updated?</h2>
        <p>The weather data is refreshed <strong>every 10-15 minutes</strong> to ensure accuracy.</p>

        <h2>🏙️ Can I Search for Any City?</h2>
        <p>Yes! Just type the name of your <strong>city, town, or even a landmark</strong>, and we’ll fetch the latest
            weather details.</p>

        <h2>🌍 What Do Air Quality Index (AQI) Numbers Mean?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>1-2 (Good):</strong> Air is clean & safe ✅</li>
            <li><strong>3-4 (Moderate):</strong> Some pollution, sensitive people take caution ⚠️</li>
            <li><strong>5-6 (Unhealthy):</strong> High pollution, avoid outdoor activities ❌</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>❓ Need More Help?</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or experience issues, feel free to <strong>refresh the page</strong>.</p>

        <p>Enjoy your day & stay weather-ready! ☀️🌧️</p>

    </div>

    {{>footer}}
</body>

</html>